Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:15.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}藏于左手的愿望终归只是愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:20.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}空梦一场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:23.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}宿于右手的空虚记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:27.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}于无人知晓的世界尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:32.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}被无尽的雨水打湿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:38.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}守护想要守护之物的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:43.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}无法相信这一切的脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:48.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}接受一切 探求明日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:51.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}勇敢之光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:56.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}伸出手去你会见到光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:03:02.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}遍体伤痕的你会看到我的光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:05.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}于高举的剑尖处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}将思绪交织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:15.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}心愿超越时空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:21.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你的勇敢之光
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== OPJP ====================
