Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:06.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如果心终会消失不再
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:10.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}至少纵声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.17,0:24:22.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恸哭和绝望之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:28.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}等待我们的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.77,0:24:35.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}都不过是生命梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.78,0:24:38.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为之奋斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.66,0:24:43.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}当下的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:50.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你哭泣的夜晚之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.13,0:24:56.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}藏有遥远未来的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.43,0:25:00.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}静谧在等待你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.10,0:25:07.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}耀眼的丘陵 必能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.23,0:25:12.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你所在的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.94,0:25:19.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}奏响你的心铃
